          "Our data informatics team gains access to your encrypted, de-identified EHR data to properly match you with relevant clinical trials.",
        icon: 'tabler:device-analytics',
      },
      {
        title: 'Step 3: <span class="font-medium">Patient receives recurring email communications</span>',
        description:
          'Our team will send you emails once every two weeks to always keep you up-to-date on the clincial trials mathcing your patient profile.',
        icon: 'tabler:mail',
      },
      {
        title: "Sit back, you're now in the loop!",
        icon: 'tabler:check',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616198814651-e71f960c3180?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=987&q=80',
